&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Zuora&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Zuora, we help businesses grow smarter and adapt faster. Our platform powers modern business models — from subscriptions and usage-based pricing to AI-driven and outcome-based offerings — helping companies launch new products, automate complex billing, and unlock predictable, recurring revenue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’ve led the Subscription Economy for more than a decade. Now we’re evolving again by building the definitive platform for quote to cash and helping companies monetize their products and services with an adaptable, AI-ready foundation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Zuora Japan, our Sales team partners with leading enterprises to drive digital transformation through subscription-based business models. We work closely with customers to help them modernize their monetization strategies and optimize revenue through Zuora’s industry-leading subscription management platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting time to join Zuora Japan. The subscription economy is accelerating rapidly, and Japanese enterprises are seeking flexible, customer-centric revenue models. As an Account Executive, you will play a critical role in expanding Zuora’s footprint in Japan by engaging with key enterprise customers, building trusted executive relationships, and driving complex sales cycles that lead to business transformation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work Arrangement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is based in Tokyo, Japan. We support a hybrid work environment, with flexibility for in-office collaboration and remote work depending on business needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join Now&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Zuora is recognized globally as a pioneer in the subscription economy, and Japan is entering a key growth phase.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will work directly with executive teams from some of Japan’s most influential companies to shape their monetization strategies.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll have access to cutting-edge tools such as Salesforce, Clari, and Zuora’s own advanced analytics to drive performance and insight.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep expertise in subscription business models and SaaS transformation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic selling at the C-level across multiple industries.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Career growth into leadership roles within a fast-growing global organization.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive new revenue growth by expanding Zuora’s presence within enterprise accounts through strategic engagement and value-based selling.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong, trust-based relationships with key customer executives to support their subscription business transformation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with Solution Engineering, Customer Success, and Marketing teams to deliver tailored business outcomes for customers.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Achieve quarterly and annual targets by managing complex sales cycles and maintaining accurate forecasting in Salesforce and Clari.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Zuora as a trusted advisor in the subscription economy, identifying opportunities for innovation and long-term partnership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
