&lt;li&gt;Integrate Systems &amp;amp; Data: Connect AI platforms with our internal tools and data sources. You’ll manage configurations, API integrations, and data pipelines to ensure the AI solutions have the information they need.. For example, you might integrate our knowledge bases or ticketing data so that the AI agents can access up-to-date company information when answering questions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
