&lt;li&gt;Lead discovery sessions focused on payment architecture, gateway strategy, authorization performance, global expansion, and operational efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design solution architectures that support flexible payment ecosystems across multiple payment providers, gateways, processors, and payment methods.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver compelling technical presentations, demonstrations, workshops, and architecture reviews tailored to executive, business, and technical audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise customers on best practices for payment orchestration, intelligent routing, payment optimization, tokenization, payment resilience, and global payment acceptance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product Management, Product Marketing, Partnerships, and Engineering to represent customer requirements and influence future product capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop reusable solution assets, reference architectures, and technical enablement materials to scale payments expertise across the organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support strategic RFPs, proof-of-concepts, and complex enterprise evaluations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
