&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong experience with cloud platforms, particularly AWS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in DevOps, SRE, and/or designing and implementing CI/CD pipelines and Kubernetes applications, utilizing technologies such as Python, Golang, and Terraform&lt;/li&gt;
